# Deployment Owner

The deployment owner username defaults to the **company display name** from admin → Company (override per install with `ADMIN_USERNAME`, comma-separated for multiple names).

Owner-only UI today:
- **Vapi sync** (`POST /api/admin/vapi`, `/vapi-sync` agent command)
- **Chat recovery** (`GET`/`POST /api/admin/chats`) — lists the distinct
  `user_id`s that own chat threads and reassigns threads orphaned under a
  previous Clerk user id (e.g. after a Clerk instance/key change) to the
  current owner. Postgres backend only.

Match is case-insensitive against the signed-in Clerk user's id (`AGENT_ALERT_USER_ID`), or `username`, `firstName`, `lastName`, full name, or primary email (full or local part).

Feature modules and admin navigation are configured per install in `config/config-{slug}.json` (not in the admin UI).
